<HEADER>
A8241 &Cx1f; tad-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WINDMILLS-$ADV06-COX     06-01 1694
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WINDMILLS-$ADV06-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FEAR OF Y2K A BOON FOR MAKERS OF WINDMILLS
 &HT;    1100&AMP;adds. Moving in (a) national and (l) lifestyle categories
for release Sunday, June 6.
 &HT;    By BOB DART
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
