</P>
<P>
   WITH: NEXT RACE BOX: A preview of Sunday's MBNA Platinum 400 at
Dover Downs International Speedway, Dover, Dela.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FOOD &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PAGE INCLUDES FOUR COLOR PHOTOGRAPHS.
</P>
<P>
   BETTER BURGERS: Summer's here and the lazy months ahead are sure
to afford many opportunities for showing off your grilling finesse,
so why not start with the basics: burgers. (Includes three color
photos of three sandwiches: Turkey Burger filled with Brie,
Open-Faced Seared Tuna Burger with Wasabi Mayonnaise and
Greek-Style Hamburgers.)
</P>
<P>
