   HKN-SABRES (Buffalo, N.Y.) _ Folo on the Buffalo Sabres' victory
over Toronto on Monday night, which puts them in the final round of
the Stanley Cup playoffs for the first time in 25 years. By Joe
LaPointe.
</P>
<P>
   GOLF-PAK (Undated) _ Se Ri Pak, who will defend her U.S. Women's
Open title, is not exactly the same person, or player, she was a
year ago. She has split with a coach, dismissed a business manager
and learned that fame and fortune always come with a price. By
Clifton Brown.
</P>
