this article. The art can be sent by mail or overnight delivery,
using your FedEx or Airborne delivery number. Please specify that
you want the art when you order the article.
 &HT;    ----------------------------------------------------
 &HT;    
 &HT;    ----- This article is also available in Spanish.-----
 &HT;    
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice _ into the
``l'' lifestyle news and ``a'' general news files.)  
 &HT;    
