<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PRESIDENTIAL-PAY02-1STLEDE-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    GROUPS WANT CANDIDATES TO OPPOSE PRESIDENTIAL PAY HIKE
 &HT;    Eds: Adds 3rd an d 4th graf from end with Alexander, Forbes
responses.
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
