 UPDATE &HT;    UPDATE
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Wednesday, June 2,
1999.
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Eds: Adds: BUCHANAN ; Deletes: OKEFENOKEE-FIRES
