   SMALLCAP-MARKETPLACE (Undated) _ Small-cap stocks are on a tear.
They even held up well the past three weeks, while the broad market
dropped about 5 percent. But can they make up all the lost ground
of the last few years? By Richard A. Oppel Jr.
</P>
