<DOCNO> NYT19990601.0327 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-01 21:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8982 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EYESIDE-FINBUDGET_SFC     06-01 0424
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EYESIDE-FINBUDGET </SLUG>
 _ SF CHRON  
 `Physician Extenders' Can Help  &HT;     By Peter Sinton 
 &HT;     c.1999 San Francisco Chronicle  
