Vice President Al Gore, right, talks with Tony Coelho, center, his
campaign chairman, on Tuesday outside a hotel after Gore and first
lady Hillary Rodham Clinton addressed a group of women supporters.
Mrs. Clinton reached out to women voters to support Gore, who lags
behind Texas Gov. George W. Bush among that group in recent polls.
(Stephen Crowley/New York Times Photo) LITE
